-- Evonik Forecasts Record Earnings This Year as Nine-Month Revenue Increases
-- B y   C h r i s t i a n e   L e n z n e r
-- 2010-11-15T08:34:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/evonik-forecasts-record-earnings-this-year-as-nine-month-revenue-increases.html
Evonik Industries AG said it expects
record earnings in 2010 after nine-month sales climbed 24
percent to 11.9 billion euros and earnings before interest and
taxes increased 93 percent to 1.7 billion euros.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christiane Lenzner at 
 clenzner@bloomberg.net  